{"tid":1102021,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"諗住老到咁上下果陣自殺","createTime":"2019-04-11T12:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T12:47:42.000Z","uid":24098,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"362627522255ae6398c6966a63cfb64a0e940b73","tid":1102021,"uid":24098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:03:45.000Z","msg":"唔想病死/意外死（如果不幸就控制唔到啦）<br />\n想同白頭到老嘅另一半<br />\n當兩個人都老到咁上下時一齊自殺<br />\n當然，前提係佢都覺得ok，同埋有幸活到果一日<br />\n我覺得咁都幾理想<br />\n大家覺得點？"},{"pid":"42865f1277ab07d15f871e21cb15073ddeb87d3e","tid":1102021,"uid":12633,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:07:14.000Z","msg":"有同樣諗法。<br />\n老左果時，人腦會自然變蠢，唔想成為on9廢老。"},{"pid":"391caff8ddf7aa501a9b9f07e9ed447c64f25d8c","tid":1102021,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:08:56.000Z","msg":"如果之後有科技所以醫百病呢"},{"pid":"eca759df58602432c454e0c4d6601c969999d838","tid":1102021,"uid":24098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42865f1277ab07d15f871e21cb15073ddeb87d3e","tid":1102021,"uid":12633,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:07:14.000Z","msg":"有同樣諗法。<br />\n老左果時，人腦會自然變蠢，唔想成為on9廢老。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:10:34.000Z","msg":"會變蠢，同埋主要唔想造成仔女負擔，<br />\n所以都諗住盡量唔洗仔女照顧咁多<br />\n<br />\n雖然到老咗可能又唔同諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暫時係咁諗"},{"pid":"12b8c4d0cc364581f3897b585a036642f115d093","tid":1102021,"uid":59269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"391caff8ddf7aa501a9b9f07e9ed447c64f25d8c","tid":1102021,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:08:56.000Z","msg":"如果之後有科技所以醫百病呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:13:25.000Z","msg":"人壽命有限 所以遇到既人同經歷過既事先會珍貴<br />\n透過科學令到自己無病無痛而變長命都無意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81ff801046390fdb62a90c2aaefb0264c76d56d","tid":1102021,"uid":24098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"391caff8ddf7aa501a9b9f07e9ed447c64f25d8c","tid":1102021,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:08:56.000Z","msg":"如果之後有科技所以醫百病呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:16:50.000Z","msg":"科技進步都唔會醫到長生不老啦，<br />\n最多咪長多2-30年命<br />\n如果話人體冷凍技術發長成熟<br />\n都要死咗先冷凍<br />\n可以約埋一齊死去冷凍嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9ac584f3cd974f8ba4c41c7aee53fe97c3e866","tid":1102021,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"391caff8ddf7aa501a9b9f07e9ed447c64f25d8c","tid":1102021,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:08:56.000Z","msg":"如果之後有科技所以醫百病呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:18:10.000Z","msg":"就算有，都唔會比一般平民用到<br />\n<br />\n一係留晒比d社會上有地位同能力的人享用 <br />\n<br />\n個個都唔死，呢個世界玩完"},{"pid":"a569b5b5e1a61ef4bae93cadca96f2f760d42da5","tid":1102021,"uid":193020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:24:20.000Z","msg":"唔錯唔錯"},{"pid":"93c1c777927d6b405f88fddf233b9f4b0adbaf18","tid":1102021,"uid":116605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:42:33.000Z","msg":"唔想等到行唔郁，食飯沖涼大小二便都要人服侍先死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想成為阻住人嘅老屎忽死廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n望住下一代咁有活力，自己就行都行唔郁，<br />\n感覺好辛苦"},{"pid":"0e89ad1badd98579b06169fd5725b0fde3efc0dd","tid":1102021,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:42:36.000Z","msg":"其實呢樣真係夾硬生存仲痛苦"},{"pid":"dbc6e21c10d1d359c8fbd693e5911931a7495625","tid":1102021,"uid":220853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f9ac584f3cd974f8ba4c41c7aee53fe97c3e866","tid":1102021,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"391caff8ddf7aa501a9b9f07e9ed447c64f25d8c","tid":1102021,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:08:56.000Z","msg":"如果之後有科技所以醫百病呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11